            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "> I think this is not desireable.  ... nvim_try_quit would then kill the terminal\n\nBut that's already the case for `:qa` . Somehow or other, clients/UIs need to quit for various purposes. A formal API removes the guesswork and allows us to build improvements into it over time.",
